reviewText: I've watched every episode of the L.I. Medium and was craving more spirit so this prompted my order. I  thought I'd be getting something similar regarding the entertainment factor but I was let down.  I believe that she has a real gift however, she was unpolished and hard to enjoy for both my wife and I.  We gave it 20 minutes then forwarded in hopes of the program changing somehow but it stayed the same all the way through.  I'm glad is was cheap!
I HAVE READ MS OBLEY'S BOOKS AND LOVE THEM.  IT WAS GOOD TO SEE HER IN ACTION WORKING WITH A GROUP.  SHE IS GOOD.  I WOULD ENJOY HAVING A READING FROM HER.
the meditation itself was very relaxing and enjoyable.  The rest of the video was a reading session.  While interesting was of no help to connecting to a spirit angel.
